Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveThe President, Major General Muhammadu Buhari (retd.) elicited laughter from footballer, Kenneth Omeruo, over their heights during a meeting in Spain on Thursday.
Buhari met with some selected Nigerians in diaspora and Nigeria football players in Spanish clubs in Madrid, Spain during his State Visit.
In a video, as Omeruo stood beside him to take pictures, the retired major general turned and said, “I hope you are not taller.”
